info.name: Web Ghosts PiPoPa
info.description: About a young boy named Akigawa Yuta who gets sucked into a virtual world through his cell phone. He meets three strange creatures that travel with him on Yuta's adventure in this strange new world.

episodes.title: Want to Go Home @ Can’t Go Home

Can't See You, Want to Meet You
To the Web World @ With You
